      "created_at": "2023-05-15T06:52:23.031Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hello</p>\n<p>I\u2019m usign Trainerday for few months now and it definitelly delivers all I need from home trainer controller, for definitelly reasonable price.<br>\nHowever until now I\u2019ve been using single-use virtual credit card to make payment. Yesterday it was refused with information that single-use cards cannot be used for renewable subscription.<br>\nWas this changed recently? Because to be honest I do not want to make subscription renewable. I\u2019d like to pay month by month (or maybe year by year later on) with such card, and I\u2019m not willing to paste any permanent (plastic or virtual) card data into the internet.<br>\nPayPal is not an option as I\u2019ve closed account few years ago due to their changes in policy.</p>\n<p>Regarda<br>\nMichal</p>",
